@startuml
title Online Quiz System

state "Register/Login" as RegisterLogin
state "Teacher" as Teacher
state "Student" as Student
state "Create Quiz" as CreateQuiz
state "Edit Quiz" as EditQuiz
state "Save/Post Quiz" as SavePostQuiz
state "View Results" as ViewResults
state "Select Quiz" as SelectQuiz
state "Answer Quiz" as AnswerQuiz
state "Submit Quiz" as SubmitQuiz
state "View Result" as ViewResult

[*] --> RegisterLogin

RegisterLogin --> Teacher : [Teacher]
RegisterLogin --> Student : [Student]

Teacher --> CreateQuiz
Teacher --> EditQuiz
Teacher --> SavePostQuiz
Teacher --> ViewResults

Student --> SelectQuiz
Student --> AnswerQuiz
Student --> SubmitQuiz
Student --> ViewResult

CreateQuiz --> SavePostQuiz
EditQuiz --> SavePostQuiz
SavePostQuiz --> ViewResults

SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult

@enduml
